2. Check for 'O' win: BFS/DFS from all 'O' in row 0. If we reach any 'O' in row `height-1`, return 'O'.
3. Check for 'X' win: BFS/DFS from all 'X' in col 0. If we reach any 'X' in col `width-1`, return 'X'.
